item.title: [RSPS] - [PI] - Need 2/3 more coders
item.dc:creator: @pkerjosh pkerjosh
item.description:
@pkerjosh wrote:

I suggest you read the rules and include pictures and more info for this you cannot just come here and request a coder… you need to

Your need to provide some sort of evidence that your development team will be successful (ie, pictures). Your work must be your own. Stealing other people's work is unacceptable and isn't tolerated here. Absolutely no advertising is allowed in this section. It is simply for recruiting people for your development team. You may discuss development here with your team, as well as discuss other features you plan on developing. If you are going to post a website, you must first get it approved with an Administrator or a Global Moderator. Failure to do this will result in an infraction for advertising.

Read this before posting: https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,393334.0.html
